ProTube is the ultimate, fully featured YouTube app. With its highly polished design, ProTube offers ad-free video with selectable playback quality, audio only playback, background playback and adjustable playback speed. You can even manage videos in playlists without signing in with a YouTube account!

With its unique audio playback mode, ProTube is the perfect audio player: Stream high quality (256kbps) audio, create playlists for songs and use ProTube as your music player! The audio playback mode uses less bandwidth than video playback and delivers higher quality audio than HD video playback. This feature is available on iOS 8 only.

Ã¢â‚¬Â¢ You can sign in with your YouTube account to view and manage your uploads, playlists and subscriptions.

Ã¢â‚¬Â¢ Discover videos, playlists and channels with the powerful search feature.

Ã¢â‚¬Â¢ Listen to entire playlists with shuffle and repeat features.
Ã¢â‚¬Â¢ Adjust the playback speed, to view certain moments in slow motion or fast forward.
Ã¢â‚¬Â¢ Mirror videos to your TV with Apple TV or Chromecast.
